Usain Bolt will become a father this year.
The legendary sprinter, the world record holder in both the 100m and 200m, announced the news on social media on Thursday, posting a picture of his pregnant girlfriend, Kasi Bennett.
The Jamaican captioned the Instagram post with: “I just want to say a KING or QUEEN is about to be HERE.”


 










